	<meta name="description" content="http://www.reddit.com/r/Guildwars2/comments/z3pzz/permanently_banned_for_buying_a_few_21_karma/ 
 
This thread is comedic gold.  In summary there was a bug that allowed people to buy racial weapons and armor for dirt cheap with Karma.  They were buying them by the hundreds and putting them into the forge to make better stuff or for salvaging.  Here is a sample. 
 
Shurrik Morosow how many did i do? any chances? thanks. did not sell anything 
 
ArenaNetSupportTeam 4 points 1 hour ago 
 
