				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Arenanet breaks out the ban hammer
				</h2>
				

						
							
							
							
						
						
				<div class="content ">
					<div id="post_message_1754678">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							<a href="http://www.reddit.com/r/Guildwars2/comments/z3pzz/permanently_banned_for_buying_a_few_21_karma/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.reddit.com/r/Guildwars2/c..._few_21_karma/</a><br />
<br />
This thread is comedic gold.  In summary there was a bug that allowed people to buy racial weapons and armor for dirt cheap with Karma.  They were buying them by the hundreds and putting them into the forge to make better stuff or for salvaging.  Here is a sample.<br />
<br />
<i>Shurrik Morosow how many did i do? any chances? thanks. did not sell anything</i><br />
<br />
[]ArenaNetSupportTeam 4 points 1 hour ago<br />
<br />
<b>You used the exploit 253 times.</b><br />
<br />
<i>Hello, my in game name is illmaculate on server henge of denvari and I was also one of those people who bought a lot of these said items. I did not know it was a exploit at the time of doing so. I reached level 54 last night and was planning on getting my tier 2 items so I headed to the tier 2 vendor in hoelbrak to see if I could finally afford any of the weapons as I knew I would reach level 60 today (I did). When I got there I noticed the great prices and thought it might be some kind of promotion or just price drop for the release, I did not think much of it but made sure to buy my level 60 items and store them in bank. I was extremely excited as I knew I would be ready. A friend of mine notified me that I could try a forge by mixing the weapons so I started doing it and creating weapons for my further levels. In my account i have a level 71 weapon and 2 80 axes and greatsword which i made sure to save for when I reach level 80. I believe I spent around 14k karma to make my weapons which is roughly 666 items. I was experimenting with the forge and having fun. I also salvaged a couple things and also saved in my bank for further use. Only items i vendor where those useless slot items due to limited space. I never even knew about it before and in my account you will only see weapons that are exactly for my warrior toon. I agree my account should be temp banned, possibly rolled back but I feel extremely bad right now that I got hit with such a huge punishment. I would never do anything like this if I knew I was breaking some huge in game law by creating myself weapons. I hope I get a reply.</i><br />
<br />
