This game is still new and I'm still figuring things out. My friend showed me how to do this and it was the first time I ever bought things with Karma so I didn't even realized how much I should have been paying. I regret what I did and I don't feel a perm ban is fair considering I didn't affect anyone directly by doing this exploit.</i><br />
